text: Rockhampton Correctional Centre (also known as Etna Creek Prison) was an Australian prison at Rockhampton, Queensland, Australia. The prison was replaced by the Capricornia Correctional Centre in 2001. ==See also== * List of prisons in Australia Category:Defunct prisons in Queensland Category:Maximum security prisons in Australia Category:Buildings and structures in Rockhampton Category:1969 establishments in Australia Category:2001 disestablishments in Australia
